{"lemma":"بَرِيئانِ","slug":"بَرِيئانِ","root":"ب.ر.#","root_slug":"ب-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَرِيء","root":"برأ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":12},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2174"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%A6%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"pure, guiltless, innocent","examples":[{"text":"وَمَن يَكْسِبْ خَطِيئَةً أَوْ إِثْمًا ثُمَّ يَرْمِ بِهِ بَرِيئًا فَقَدِ ٱحْتَمَلَ بُهْتَانًا وَإِثْمًا مُّبِينًا","english":"But whoever earns an offense or a sin and then blames it on an innocent [person] has taken upon himself a slander and manifest sin."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"disassociated","examples":[{"text":"كَمَثَلِ ٱلشَّيْطَانِ إِذْ قَالَ لِلْإِنْسَانِ ٱكْفُرْ فَلَمَّا كَفَرَ قَالَ إِنِّي بَرِيءٌ مِنْكَ إِنِّي أَخَافُ اللّٰهَ رَبَّ الْعَالَمِينَ"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"recovered, cured"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2174","headword_ar":"بَرِىْءٌ","root":"brA^","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Free,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely a fault, defect, imperfection, blemish, or vice; (Mgh, Msb;) and, also followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quit, of it; irresponsible for it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of immunity with respect to it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exempt from the demand thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely a debt, (Msb,) or a claim, or due, or right; (Mgh;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAriYN","text_ar":"بَارِىٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='N","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA bariYo'N minohu","text_ar":"اَنَا بَرِىْءٌ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am free from it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; (T, * S, M, K; *) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraA='N","text_ar":"بَرَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", used alike as sing. and dual and pl. (Fr, T, S, M, K) and masc. and fem., (Fr, T, M, K,) because it is originally an inf. n.; (Fr, T, S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraA='N","text_ar":"بُرَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariYo'N","text_ar":"بَرِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyw^uwna","text_ar":"بَرِيوُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraA^'u","text_ar":"بُرَاءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraA='N","text_ar":"بُرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, K,) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEaAlN","text_ar":"فُعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxaAlN","text_ar":"رُخَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) of an extr. measure, disapproved by Suh, who says, in the R, that it is a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraA^'u","text_ar":"بُرَاءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and has tenween because it resembles [words originally of the measure]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEaAlN","text_ar":"فُعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and that the rel. n. formed from it is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraAwiY~N","text_ar":"بُرَاوِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) but it is mentioned by AAF as a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariYo'N","text_ar":"بَرِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and as being like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxaAlN","text_ar":"رُخَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and Fr mentions"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraA='u","text_ar":"بُرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a pl. of the same, imperfectly decl., with one of the two hemzehs suppressed, (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biraA='N","text_ar":"بِرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboraA='N","text_ar":"اَبْرَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboriy^aA='u","text_ar":"اَبْرِيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,) the last two anomalous: (TA:) the fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyo'N","text_ar":"بَرِيْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyoy^apN","text_ar":"بَرِيْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariyoA=tN","text_ar":"بَرِيْا=تٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariy~aAtN","text_ar":"بَرِيَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraAyaA","text_ar":"بَرَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, S, M, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA bariYo'N minohu","text_ar":"اَنَا بَرِىْءٌ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliY~N minohu","text_ar":"خَلِىٌّ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am free from it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, more commonly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quit, of it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^naA baraA='N","text_ar":"انَا بَرَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaA='N minohu","text_ar":"خَلَا=ءٌ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu","text_ar":"مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA AlbaraA='u","text_ar":"اَنَا البَرَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHonu minoka AlbaraA='u","text_ar":"نَحْنُ مِنْكَ البَرَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxalaA='u","text_ar":"الخَلَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We are clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quit, of you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Fr, T;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awuw AlbaraA='i","text_ar":"ذَوُو البَرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so says Aboo-Is-hák; and As says the like of what Fr says. (T.) It is said in the Kur [xliii. 25],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mim~aA taEobuduwna","text_ar":"مِمَّا تَعْبُدُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~aniY baraA='N","text_ar":"اـِنَّنِى بَرَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily I am clear of that which ye worship"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, M;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariYo'N","text_ar":"بَرِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buraA='N","text_ar":"بُرَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; accord. to different readers. (Bd.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bariYo'N","text_ar":"بَرِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in several places in the Kur. (M.) Accord. to IAar, it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clear of evil qualities"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispositions; shunning what is vain and false; remote from actions that occasion suspicion; pure in heart from associating any with God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound in body and intellect."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAriy^N","text_ar":"بَارِيٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["Msb","Fr","T","S","M","K","TA","Lh"]}]}}